Non-Stationarity Sleep Dataset

Whitney

2/21/2020

Read ABD, THO, CFlow, Sleep Stage into R

library(R.matlab)

abd_mFile <- paste(1:20, "/ABD.mat", sep = "")
abd <- paste("ABD-", 1:20, sep = "")

tho_mFile <- paste(1:20, "/THO.mat", sep = "")
tho <- paste("THO-", 1:20, sep = "")

cflow_mFile <- paste(1:20, "/CFlow.mat", sep = "")
cflow <- paste("CFlow-", 1:20, sep = "")

stage_mFile <- paste(1:20, "/STAGE.mat", sep = "")
stage <- paste("Stage-", 1:20, sep = "")

for (i in 1:20){
  assign(abd[i], readMat(abd_mFile[i]))
  assign(tho[i], readMat(tho_mFile[i]))
  assign(cflow[i], readMat(cflow_mFile[i]))
  assign(stage[i], readMat(stage_mFile[i]))
}

Plot CFlow vs. ABD and THO

plot(1:10000/100, `CFlow-1`$CFlow[1:10000],
     type = "l", xlab = "Time (sec)",
     ylab = "Flow", las = 1,
     col = "red")
lines(1:10000/100, `ABD-1`$ABD[1:10000],
      col = "blue")
lines(1:10000/100, `THO-1`$THO[1:10000],
      col = "green")

plot(1:10000/100, `CFlow-10`$CFlow[1:10000],
     type = "l", xlab = "Time (sec)",
     ylab = "Flow", las = 1,
     col = "red")
lines(1:10000/100, `ABD-10`$ABD[1:10000],
      col = "blue")
lines(1:10000/100, `THO-10`$THO[1:10000],
      col = "green")

plot(1:10000/100, `CFlow-20`$CFlow[1:10000],
     type = "l", xlab = "Time (sec)",
     ylab = "Flow", las = 1,
     col = "red")
lines(1:10000/100, `ABD-20`$ABD[1:10000],
      col = "blue")
lines(1:10000/100, `THO-20`$THO[1:10000],
